description: Summary tab missing-data warnings — one mark, one tooltip, unified aggregator
globs: AltArmy_TBC/Tabs/TabSummary.lua,AltArmy_TBC/Data/SummaryData.lua,spec/Data/SummaryData_spec.lua
alwaysApply: false
